title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Feb 4 2022

description:
Alex Berenson joins Clay and Buck to deliver the covid latest: good political news, but bad medical news. Montage of CNN reporting misinformation. Senator Ted Cruz joins Clay and Buck to discuss the Olympics in China, the border fiasco, and Democrat covid hypocrisy. C&B close out the week with callers.
